dnl Check for libraries
dnl ===================

GLIB_REQ=2.66.0
GMODULE_REQ=2.0.0
GTK_REQ=2.24.0
GIO_REQ=2.0
UNIQUE_REQ=0.9.3
EXIV2_REQ=0.14
TAGLIB_REQ=1.4
LIBGSF_REQ=1.12.0
POPPLER_REQ=0.18

AC_SUBST(GLIB_REQ)
AC_SUBST(GTK_REQ)
AC_SUBST(GIO_REQ)
AC_SUBST(UNIQUE_REQ)
AC_SUBST(EXIV2_REQ)
